g.text: Spring Batch Components - Reader, Processor, Writer Details

text.tspan: Each component in a Spring Batch Step has specific responsibilities.
All three work together ATOMICALLY per chunk:
- If any item in a chunk fails, the entire chunk is rolled back
✓ WRITE: Write all items in one transaction
- Called for each item from reader
- Example: Write 23 valid customers in one batch
- All items succeed or all fail
- Writes 25 items in one SQL batch
